metatags.og:title: Supreme Court upholds Texas law requiring ID to access adult websites
metatags.og:description: The Supreme Court upheld a Texas law intended to protect minors from sexually explicit content, ruling that requiring ID to verify age is a reasonable measure despite concerns about the privacy of adult users. Pornhub and other companies that operate adult websites challenged the law.
